                    textOnly="&lt;h3>IN THIS ARTICLE&lt;/h3>&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;span class=&quot;body-copy-large&quot;>HPE enabled Saudi Payments to launch the countries first local mobile payment system&lt;/span>&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;span class=&quot;body-copy-large&quot;>HPE Synergy and 3PAR solutions provide the “highest levels of application performance”&lt;/span>&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;span class=&quot;body-copy-large&quot;>Saudi Payments project deemed as a significant digital transformation as part of its Vision 2030&lt;/span>&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xa;"
